      <h2>Better Access</h2>
      <p class="larger-body-font">Keeping it free for all, including employers, HireMe is more open to smaller local shops that normally would
        pass up on doing much more then putting a sign out front of their store. A larger broader community brings more flexible
        job opportunities.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
